WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:11.688
A harness for coding agents
StatePort runs agents like Codex headlessly and gives the work a durable home outside the chat.

00:00:12.138 --> 00:00:23.871
The application you get
Open a named project. Your state files and decisions live here, not hidden inside a session.

00:00:24.321 --> 00:00:36.177
The agent is replaceable
Ask the agent for help in conversation. The work does not live or die with the chat.

00:00:36.627 --> 00:00:46.261
Know what you can trust
See what is ready, what is being checked, and what is only a test.

00:00:46.711 --> 00:00:51.311
Take it with you
The same project stays readable on a small screen.

00:00:51.761 --> 00:01:01.985
Local preview
A local preview - not yet a public release. Harness the agent, govern what it does, keep the work.
